{
  "stem": "2002.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I took my-- my mother and I say, let's go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We gonna to go to [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Brunitsza. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Brunitza ?] is a little farm area where my father would deal with the people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we know a lot of farmers there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were-- we considered them as friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I took my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But the bridge was bombed, a little bridge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I couldn't cross over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I don't swim.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was a river.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And somehow, I remember there was a little small boat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And somehow I pushed my mother in, and I got in there and somebody would pushed out, whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we crossed over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "From there we were walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was walking, and the planes kept coming and bombing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So it was on the road to [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Brunitza, ?] was a big bush.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The bush maybe was about five, six foot tall, but very big.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I took my mother and I pushed her in the bush in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I went in, and we were laying there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I heard the bombs comin' down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say the bombs came down maybe between 20 feet, 30 feet, 40 feet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I kept moving my feet all the time, and I kept asking my mother, how you feel?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I thought maybe a shrapnel hit us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I looked through the bush, I looked out, I could see cows falling down, being machine-gunned down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after the planes left, we were laying there for five minutes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after five minutes, it looked like this is over, and I got out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as I got out, I kept looking the road behind us and the front-- and the front of us was craters.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
